Class TessBaseAPI.PageIteratorLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.tesseract.android.TessBaseAPI.PageIteratorLevel
  • Enclosing class:
    TessBaseAPI

    public static final class TessBaseAPI.PageIteratorLevel
extends Object
    Elements of the page hierarchy, used in ResultIterator to provide functions that operate on each level without having to have 5x as many functions.

    NOTE: At present RIL_PARA and RIL_BLOCK are equivalent as there is no paragraph internally yet.
